ures/460x307/4/9/3/533493_gettyimages1247929159_815161.jpg" srcset="https://d2cbg94ubxgsnp.cloudfront.net/Pictures/460x307/4/9/3/533493_gettyimages1247929159_815161.jpg 460w,https://d2cbg94ubxgsnp.cloudfront.net/Pictures/306x204/4/9/3/533493_gettyimages1247929159_815161.jpg 306w,https://d2cbg94ubxgsnp.cloudfront.net/Pictures/360x240/4/9/3/533493_gettyimages1247929159_815161.jpg 360w,https://d2cbg94ubxgsnp.cloudfront.net/Pictures/100x67/4/9/3/533493_gettyimages1247929159_815161.jpg 100w" width="460" height="307" /></a></p><div class="subSleeve"><h2><a href="https://www.chemistryworld.com/news/rail-company-will-pay-600-million-to-settle-east-palestine-lawsuits/4019307.article">Rail company will pay $600 million to settle East Palestine lawsuits</a></h2><p class="meta"><span class="author">By <a rel="author" href="https://www.chemistryworld.com/rebecca-trager/1905.bio">Rebecca Trager</a></span></p></div></div></div><div class="spinLayout half onecol left item-third"><div class="sleeve"><p class="picture"><a href="https://www.chemistryworld.com/news/66-million-settlement-follows-2019-fire-at-texas-petrochemical-facility/4019271.article" class="image"><img alt="Petrochemical fire at the Intercontinental Terminals Company in Deer Park, Texas" class="lazyloaded" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width:479px) 100vw, (max-width:767px) 50vw, (max-width:1023px) 306px, 174px" src="https://d2cbg94ubxgsnp.cloudfront.net/Pictures/460x307/2/1/4/533214_2mk5987_329557_crop.jpg" srcset="https://d2cbg94ubxgsnp.cloudfront.net/Pictures/460x307/2/1/4/533214_2mk5987_329557_crop.jpg 460w,https://d2cbg94ubxgsnp.cloudfront.net/Pictures/306x204/2/1/4/533214_2mk5987_329557_crop.jpg 306w,https://d2cbg94ubxgsnp.cloudfront.net/Pictures/360x240/2/1/4/533214_2mk5987_329557_crop.jpg 360w,https://d2cbg94ubxgsnp.cloudfront.net/Pictures/100x67/2/1/4/533214_2mk5987_329557_crop.jpg 100w" width="460" height="307" /></a></p><div class="subSleeve"><h2><a href="https://www.chemistryworld.com/news/66-million-settleme